{CHARACTER_NAME}: MR. MILLER
{DIALOGUE}: Compared to me she is.
{DIALOGUE}: How
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: come you're not at the cash anymore?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They catch ya steal- ing?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SARAH
