{DIALOGUE}: What's it to ya?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: When she leaves, the old man is grinning, behind the menu, where no one can see him.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 36 INT. BIG BOB'S/SERVICE CORRIDOR
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah rounds the corner, walking fast as she undoes her apron.
