{DIALOGUE}: Okay, let's see...Got a pos- itive on her.
{DIALOGUE}: She's Sarah Connor, works as a legal--
{CHARACTER_NAME}: VUKOVICH
{META_DATA}: (interrupting)
{DIALOGUE}: That can't be right.
