{CHARACTER_NAME}: ANCHORMAN (V.O.)
{META_DATA}: (continuing)
{DIALOGUE}: ...and this almost identical killing two hours ago of a Venice resident with virtually the same name.
{DIALOGUE}: Sarah Ann Connor, a 24 year old legal secretary, was pronounced dead at the scene in her beachfront apartment...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A customer gestures for the bartender's attention.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CUSTOMER
{DIALOGUE}: Hey, can we change this and catch the ball scores.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BARTENDER
{META_DATA}: (reaching for the knob)
{DIALOGUE}: Sure.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah leaps half over the bar, startling everyone.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SARAH
{META_DATA}: (shouting)
{DIALOGUE}: Leave it where it is!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ANCHORMAN (V.O.)
