{DIALOGUE}: This is a mistake.
{DIALOGUE}: I haven't done anything.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: REESE
{DIALOGUE}: No.
{DIALOGUE}: But you will.
{DIALOGUE}: It's very important that you live.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah closes her eyes, as if to shut it all out.
