{DIALOGUE}: That Terminator is out there.
{DIALOGUE}: It can't be reasoned with, it can't be bargained with...it doesn't feel pity of remorse or fear... and it absolutely will not stop.
{DIALOGUE}: Ever.
{DIALOGUE}: Until you are dead.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah slump in utter resignation.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SARAH
{META_DATA}: (quietly)
{DIALOGUE}: Can you stop it?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reese doesn't look at her.
