{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 139 EXT. PARKING LOT - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reese's car launches forward from its space, tires spinning as Terminator fires from the window of the cruiser.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 140 INT. BUICK - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The rear window explodes and Reese ducks, then cranks the wheel.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 141 EXT. PARKING LOT - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reese and Terminator race along opposite sides of a row of cars, approaching the exit.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The cruiser pulls ahead and closes diagonally as they clear the last car.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reese sees the other's shotgun leveled.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He ducks, steering blind, keeps it floored.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The windshield and side window EXPLODES INWARD.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Buick slams into the black-and-white, spinning it into a parked truck.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: TIRES SCREAM as the two cars slew around heading for the exit.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SEVERAL ANGLES, as the police react.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The chopper banks tight and dives across the tops of the parked cars.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Cruisers race to converge.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 143 EXT. STREET - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LOW WIDE ANGLE, PRECEDING REESE'S BUICK as it hits the street, accelerating.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Terminator's cruiser slides out behind it, fishtails, races forward.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Engines roar as the cars go flat out.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Buildings lining the street become a blur.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The chopper arcs in behind them.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Legitimate police, lights blazing, enter the pursuit one by one.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LOW ANGLE, MOVING WITH TERMINATOR'S CAR as Reese dodges across all lanes ahead of it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Terminator gaining.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They run an intersection at a hundred plus.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 144 INT. BUICK - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reese is feeding his last two shells into the riot gun.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: REESE
{META_DATA}: (yelling)
{DIALOGUE}: Steer!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Holding the gun is both hands he leans out the window, still keeping the throttle mashed down.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah grabs the wheel, fighting to control the car.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 145 EXT. STREET/BUICK - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: MOVING WITH THE BUICK, looking back, as Reese aims the shotgun, buffeted by the windstream.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Terminator's car, B.G., overtakes rapidly.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SARAH
{META_DATA}: (shouting)
{DIALOGUE}: Reese!
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 146 INT. BUICK - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: OVER SARAH'S SHOULDER as they approach an intersection... red light their way and an ALPHA BETA TRUCK entering cross wise.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 147 EXT. STREET/CARS - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Past Terminator, F.G., his shotgun aimed as he comes along side...at Reese.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They are staring down each other's barrels.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 148 INT. BUICK - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah grabs the shift lever.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: DETAIL - SHIFTER, as she slams it into reverse.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 149 EXT. STREET/CARS - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: MOVING WITH BOTH CARS as the Buick skids with rear tires locked.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reese and Terminator FIRE simultaneously.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: TIGHT ON REESE as the doorpost next to his shoulder is torn out by the other's blast.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ON TERMINATOR, leaning to see around his shattered wind- shield.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Too late.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He hurtles into the intersection, past the skidding Buick.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Clips the back of the semi.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Spins radically.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Vaults the curb in a screeching front-end roll.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WHIP-PANNING WITH THE CRUISER as it crashes upside-down through the counter area of an A & W.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LOW ANGLE as Reese and Sarah slide to a stop in a cloud of tire smoke.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Transmission fluid pours out of the car like blood.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: An instant later they are surrounded by an assortment of LAPD, SHERIFF'S DEPT., and CHP CARS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The helicopter hovers overhead.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: MEDIUM ON SARAH AND REESE, he raises his hands, through the side window, in plain sight.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A phalanx of cops, guns drawn, approaches the car warily.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah looks at Reese.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Then at the cops.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She opens the door and runs, staggering, toward them.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Vukovich steps forward and pulls her away to safety.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: C.U. - REESE watching her go as a cop eases his door open.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 150 EXT. A & W - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Two cops approach the overturned squad car jammed into the wreckage of the small building.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They shine their flashlights inside.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It is empty.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The cyborg has VANISHED.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A sign which reads 'DRIVE IN' detaches from an awning and crashed down across the crushed auto.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 151 INT. VUKOVICH'S OFFICE - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah, huddles in a blanket, is siting on a bench opposite Vukovich's desk.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Motionless.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Her eyes are fixed on the middle distance.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She's been crying.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Now she's emptied out.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The door opens.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: At the sound of the latch Sarah jerks as if struck, and cringes involuntarily.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Vukovich enters with Traxler and DR. PETER SILBERMAN, a criminal psychologist.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Silberman is smooth of skin and manner, young, ambitious and...fat.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He is enthusiastic about the workings of the human psyche, as emotionally involved as someone pulling the wings off a fly.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Vukovich sits beside Sarah and hands her a cup of coffee.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He puts a paternal arm around her shoulders.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: VUKOVICH
{DIALOGUE}: Here, drink some of this...
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SARAH
