{DIALOGUE}: Lieutenant, are you sure it's them?
{DIALOGUE}: Maybe I should see the ...bodies.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: VUKOVICH
{DIALOGUE}: They've already been identi- fied.
{DIALOGUE}: There's no doubt.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah begins to cry again, slowly and very quickly.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SARAH
{META_DATA}: (to herself)
{DIALOGUE}: Of, God...Ginger...kiddo, I'm so sorry.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Vukovich takes the coffee cup from her as her arms sag and it starts to spill.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: VUKOVICH
{META_DATA}: (gently)
{DIALOGUE}: Sarah.
{META_DATA}: (pause)
{DIALOGUE}: Sarah, this is Dr. Silber- man.
{DIALOGUE}: I'd like you to tell him everything Reese said to you.
{DIALOGUE}: Do you feel up to it?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SARAH
{META_DATA}: (almost in- audible)
{DIALOGUE}: I guess so.
