{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 160 INT. POLICE DEPARTMENT FOYER - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Silberman can be seen through a glass partition next to the bullet-proof glass booth enclosing the NIGHT DESK SERGEANT'S counter.
