{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: There are conventional military vehicles as well.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He passes several family groups.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Gaunt kids are huddles around an old TV SET.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Its glow bathes them.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: REVERSE ANGLE reveals that the set has been gutted and a small cookfire crackles inside the shell.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Nearby a kid has a LARGE RAT cornered and is whacking it with a stick.
