{DIALOGUE}: Whaddya say?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He picks up her sign and they look at each other for a second, then get up.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 194 INT. TERMINATOR'S HOTEL ROOM - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Terminator sits in his room with the blinds drawn tight.
