{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: C.U. - TERMINATOR
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: his eyes tracking rapidly.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: His skin is waxy, WHITE, BRUISED, GANGRENOUS in places.
