{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 194A/FX POV - TERMINATOR 194A/FX
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Showing Sarah's book.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: In microseconds the handwritten entries are translated into CRT-type characters and displayed to one side of the screen.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: This updates instantly as the page is turned.
