{DIALOGUE}: I have to, man.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 235 EXT. FREEWAY/TANKER
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE UNDER THE REAR TRAILER
