{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 236 EXT. FREEWAY OVERPASS - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah watches the truck roll on without leaving a body in its wake.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She feels a premonitory dread.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 237 EXT. FREEWAY/TANKER - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Beneath the braking semi, Terminator CRAWLS UPSIDE DOWN, hand over hand like a HUMAN FLY, toward CAMERA.
