{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: As the pavement stops beneath him he drops off and rolls out from under the truck.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 238 INT. TANKER CAB - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The driver looks around in astonishment as his door is ripped open.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Terminator appears.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A grisly apparition.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: FLINGS THE DRIVER OUT and takes his place behind the wheel.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Ignoring the terrified partner, he examines the controls.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 238/FX POV - TERMINATOR 238/FX
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: In digitized cyborg-vision we see an ABSTRACT OF THE INSTRUMENTS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The shift lever is extended graphically down into a three-dimensional SCHEMATIC OF THE TRANS- MISSION.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Analytical DATA PRINTS OUT RAPID-FIRE.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 239 EXT. FREEWAY OVERPASS - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: From the railing Sarah sees the tanker below as
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: a body falls beside it, rolling.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The truck swings in a slow arc.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: TEARS THROUGH THE DIVIDING FENCE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Heads back toward her on the wrong side of the freeway.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She stares in numb horror.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The nightmare refuses to end.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She runs to the crippled pickup and sees a front tire flat, shredded by a crumpled fender.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She searches the cab frantically for the KEYS TO THE MOTORCYCLES.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Finds them above the sun visor.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah leaps into the bed of the pickup and attacks the motorcycle strap-downs frantically.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Panting with terror she rolls the bike off the truck.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It crashes on its side and she falls on it painfully.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Straining until she CRIES OUT INVOLUNTARILY, she lifts it upright.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KICKS the engine over.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LOW ANGLE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: as the tanker crashes back through the divider and starts UP THE OVERPASS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah is trapped in that concrete corridor.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She kicks for her life.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The bike catches for a moment.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Dies.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The truck BELLOWS, down-shifting on the curving grade.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah kicks again and again, crying out with each stroke.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Again and again, furiously.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The engine CATCHES.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SARAH
{META_DATA}: (rapidly)
{DIALOGUE}: Come on, come on, come on ...run, you...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The bike runs with a healthy roar.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LOW ANGLE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: up the face of the tractor-trailer, the retaining wall blur- ring by.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Terminator's red eye can be seen through the wind- shield.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah drags Reese, stumbling,to the bike, props him on the seat behind her.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He clutches the satchel weakly.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SARAH
{DIALOGUE}: Hold on real tight, okay?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She guns the engine and roars off.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LOW ANGLE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: as the tanker demolishes the pickup a moment later, TOSSING IT OVER THE SIDE LIKE A BEER CAN.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 240 EXT. FREEWAY - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah hits level freeway with a quarter-mile lead on the tanker, distant B.G., but the little bike is overloaded and she can't coax it above seventy-five.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON TANKER roaring forward, shifting up through the gears.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON SARAH AND KYLE, his head lolling on her shoulder.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He starts to fall sideways.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SARAH
{META_DATA}: (shouting)
{DIALOGUE}: Hold on, goddamnit!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He rouses slightly, gripping her tighter.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: HIGH ANGLE - MOVING WITH BOTH VEHICLES as Sarah starts to ZIGZAG desperately across all four lanes.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The truck stays with her, closing, its trailer WHIPLASHING VIOLENTLY.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 241 EXT./INT. TUNNEL - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The truck is right behind them as then enter a TUNNEL.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A half-mile of exitless concrete and strobing fluorescent lights.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: M.C.U. - SARAH AND KYLE (PROCESS SHOT) - He blinks and looks back at a SOLID WALL OF METAL AND LIGHTS looming behind them.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah hunches down.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They hit eighty.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: FULL SHOT - The leviathan dwarfs them, its big tires ROARING like the hubs of Hell.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 242 EXT. FREEWAY - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The tanker is twenty feet behind them as they clear the tunnel.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah dodges to one side and LOCKS THE BRAKES.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The bike slides, fish-tailing.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The truck roars past, hitting the air-brakes.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The trailers force her closer and closer to the guardrail as Terminator tries to sandwich her.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The bike slides to a stop.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The rearmost set of trailer wheels slams into the guardrail right in front of Sarah.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah emerges from a cloud of tire smoke, cutting across all four lances behind the stopped semi.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 243 EXT. FREEWAY EMBANKMENT - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah tries to ride down the steep embankment but loses control, spilling the bike.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She and Kyle tumble down the slope.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: MOVING WITH HER as she scrambles, half-dragging Kyle, through a row of trees at a chainlink retaining fence.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She crawls under the fence, tugs Kyle and the satchel through after.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah looks up at the source of a SUDDEN THUNDEROUS ROAR.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 243/FX ANGLE ON TANKER 243/FX
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It appears above them, grinding over the embankment.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It rolls down the steep slope TOWARD CAMERA, FLATTENING TREES.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 244 EXT. INDUSTRIAL SITE - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah and Kyle scramble up and run across the STORAGE LOT of a MODERN FACTORY COMPLEX of LOW BUILDINGS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Kyle struggles to keep up, holding the satchel.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LIKE A JUGGERNAUT the truck follows, smashing through parked cars and FLATTENING A PRE-FAB STORAGE BUILDING.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They enter an alley-like space between two buildings.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Kyle is fumbling to open the satchel.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE BACK as the tanker enters the alley.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It TEARS THE CORNER OFF ONE BUILDING as it turns in.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Terminator looks down from his mountain of steel.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 245 INT. TANKER CAB - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: OVER TERMINATOR'S SHOULDER, looking down at a tiny figure below, running in the headlights' glare.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It is Sarah, alone.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 246 EXT. ALLEY - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reese crouches in a TRASH-DUMPSTER which is sandwiched between the wall and the tanker.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: There are only inches of clearance as the trailers pass by.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He lights a PIPE CHARGE, jumps up and wedges it under the tank-cylinder of the second trailer.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He ducks as it rolls on.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah is stumbling in the glare of the truck's lights.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: E.C.U. - PIPE BOMB, the fuse burning.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: M.C.U. - TERMINATOR, through the windshield, his eye glowing.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: C.U. - REESE huddles in the dumpster.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 247/FX LOW WIDE ANGLE ON SARAH AND TRAILER (PROCESS SHOT) 247/FX
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The REAR TRAILER EXPLODES.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: An unbelievable FIREBALL ERUPTS SKYWARD, silhouetting Sarah's running figure F.G.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The dumpster is enveloped by fire and hurled, rolling, down the alley.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah makes it around a corner as the FORWARD TRAILER EXPLODES and an OCEAN OF FLAME rolls forward, blasting by her.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The dumpster topples and Kyle rolls out, surrounded by fire.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 248/FX SEQUENCE - TERMINATOR 248/FX
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: In the center of the inferno Terminator struggles violently.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: His FLESH FIRES AND SIZZLES.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He tears loose from the TWISTED WRECKAGE and collapses to the ground.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sinks into a CHARRED MASS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: STOPS MOVING.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: C.U. - TERMINATOR, mouth open, skull-like, motionless in the flames.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 249 EXT. ALLEY - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah crawls away from the intense heat and lies watching the motionless figure in the blaze.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 250 EXT. ALLEY/FAR END - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah rounds the corner, staggering, searching.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She sees Kyle crumpled face-down near the dumpster, sheltered from the heat by its mass.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She drags his away.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Rolls him over.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: C.U. - REESE, his head lolls.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He opens his eyes
{CHARACTER_NAME}: REESE
{META_DATA}: (weakly)
{DIALOGUE}: Sarah.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SARAH
{DIALOGUE}: We did it, Kyle.
{DIALOGUE}: We got it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She hugs him.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 250/FX FULL SHOT (PROCESS) 250/FX
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They hold the embrace, silhouetted by the diminishing flames.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It would be a wonderful final image.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Except...TERMINATOR STAGGERS OUT OF THE BLAZE BEHIND THEM.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: M.C.U. - TERMINATOR, the last flakes of flesh are falling from him like burning leaves.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: His gleaming structure is revealed in all its intricacy.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: No longer a 'He', but an 'It'.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It looks like Death rendered in steel.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A CHROME SKELETON with HYDRAULIC MUSCLES and TENDONS OF FLEXIBLE CABLE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: In the sockets of the metal skull, the eyeball swivels with a WHIR of tiny servos, both glowing red now.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It turns slowly and fixes its gaze directly INTO CAMERA.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 251 EXT. ALLEY - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: C.U. - SARAH - She chokes on a scream, crams knuckles in her mouth.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: FULL SHOT (FX), as the machine takes a step toward them, dragging one MALFUNCTIONING LEG.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: PANAGLIDE WITH KYLE AND SARAH as they stagger to their feet and run to the nearest building.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They come to a glass door.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Kyle kicks it in.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Unlatches it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They enter dark OFFICES to the sound of ALARMS and DISTANT SIRENS.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 252 INT. CORRIDORS - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah and Kyle run down a corridor.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Through a door, which they close and lock.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They move off down a cross-corridor.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Terminator BLASTS THE DOOR OFF ITS HINGES, F.G., and staggers through.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It starts after their receding figures as they round the corner at the end of the hall.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 253 INT. OPEN OFFICES - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Wracked, exhausted, they stumble through a maze of PARTI- TIONED OFFICE CUBICLES.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 254 INT. CORRIDOR - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Terminator catches sight of them through a floor-to- ceiling window.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It makes an unhesitating right turn through the glass.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 255 INT. OPEN OFFICES - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah and Kyle look back at the sound of SHATTERING GLASS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: PANAGLIDE PRECEDING THE TERMINATOR as it crashes forward, line-of-sight, through the maze.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It splinters partitions.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Flings desks out of the way.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: FOLLOWING SARAH AND KYLE as they reach a heavy FIREDOOR and go through.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 256 INT. MANUFACTURING AREA - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Kyle slides the bolts on the metal firedoor.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Behind them are acres of machinery in darkness.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Silence.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CRASH!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Terminator hits the door from the far side.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Hinges SQUEAL.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Kyle goes to a LARGE BREAKER PANEL and opens it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Starts throwing switches.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Behind them, machines START UP ONE BY ONE.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SARAH
{META_DATA}: (panting)
{DIALOGUE}: What are you doing?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: REESE
{META_DATA}: (weakly)
{DIALOGUE}: Cover...our footsteps...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He sags, sliding down the wall.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She pulls him up.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Half-carries him into the maze of machines.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The dark gallery is filled with WHIRRING, CLANKING SHAPES, SHATTERING CONVEYER BELTS and improbable mechanisms lashing mindlessly.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reese slips to the floor and Sarah is no longer able to support him.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: REESE
{META_DATA}: (faintly)
{DIALOGUE}: Leave me here.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah crouches beside him.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Grabs his shirt front.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Yells over the machines.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SARAH
{DIALOGUE}: I'm not leaving you anywhere you jerk.
{DIALOGUE}: Haven't you figured it out?
{DIALOGUE}: Kyle, John is our son.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reese's eyes refocus.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SARAH
{META_DATA}: (continuing)
{DIALOGUE}: There isn't going to be anybody else...I don't want anybody else.
{DIALOGUE}: Listen to me!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She pauses, then resumes in a commanding, military shout.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SARAH
{META_DATA}: (continuing)
{DIALOGUE}: Move!
{DIALOGUE}: Reese!
{DIALOGUE}: Let's go.
{DIALOGUE}: Move you ass!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She drags him to his feet and he staggers on.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Hinges SHATTER and the firedoor is hurled inward.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Terminator scans the darkness.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE - PANNING WITH SARAH AND KYLE as they move through the machines.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The cyborg steps forward, scanning methodically.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah and Kyle move in a crouch through the treacherous tangle of pipes and machinery.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Kyle picks up a length of pipe to use as a weapon.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: As they climb out onto a cat- walk between the two huge mechanisms, Sarah clambers over an innocuous CONTROL PANEL.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Her knee inadvertently hits a RED PUSH BUTTON.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: With a ROAR the stamping-plate of a HYDRAULIC PRESS slams down an inch from her hand.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Startled, she tumbles to the catwalk.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Terminator's eyes swivel as he hears the single non- rhythmic sound.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Kyle and Sarah run to the end of the catwalk, but find the door there locked.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SARAH
{DIALOGUE}: Come on!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They double back to escape the cul-de-sac.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Terminator steps in front of them, cutting them off.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: REESE
{META_DATA}: (shouting)
{DIALOGUE}: Run!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He pushes Sarah roughly and she stumbles away.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Kyle raises the pipe with his good arm as the Terminator advances.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: REESE
{META_DATA}: (over his shoulder)
{DIALOGUE}: Run, damn it!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She hesitates, backing away.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The cyborg swings at Reese STEEL CLANGS ON STEEL.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Kyle strikes and parries but is sledgehammered back.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON CATWALK as Kyle lands in a heap, smashed against a stanchion of the railing which prevented him falling to the factory floor twenty feet below.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah turns and runs.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LOW ANGLE PAST REESE, F.G., as the cyborg approaches him.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: E.C.U. - A FUSE BURNING.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: C.U. - KYLE'S FACE streaked with blood, pressed to the floor as a metal foot CLANGS DOWN, F.G. His eyes snap open.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah falls, gets up, runs on.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Terminator draws back for a death blow.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: And Kyle rolls with the last of his strength, raising the pipe bomb he has been cradling.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He jams it between two hydraulic cylinders just beneath the cyborg's armored rib- cage.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Then rolls off the catwalk.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Terminator has an instant to react, reaching for the bomb, before it EXPLODES.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah is pitched forward by the blast and slides on the floor.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Slams up against one wall.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A withering spray of shrapnel strafes the walls around her.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Pieces of scrap metal clatter throughout the factory, rain- ing down.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: C.U. - SARAH, very still.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She winces and opens her eyes.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Slowly looks up.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: POV - SARAH, as the smoke clears.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Terminator is GONE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Unrecognizable clumps of BURNING DEBRIS lie scattered about.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Looking down through the grating floor she sees Kyle's body.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LOW ANGLE ON KYLE F.G., Sarah on catwalk above.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Kyle's eyes are half-open.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Still.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: His face peaceful.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON ONE OF THE FIRES climbing some plastic tubing and triggering a SPRINKLER HEAD.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It begins to rain.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: C.U. - SARAH sitting up as the water runs over her.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She looks down.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Protruding from her right thigh is a TWISTED PIECE OF METAL.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Shrapnel.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Part of the cyborg.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She pulls it out, grimacing.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Her leg is broken.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It is a long time before she can gather the will to move.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SARAH'S POV - She sees a WALL PHONE several yards away, beyond the debris from the explosion.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She starts to crawl toward it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She passes A LARGE CLUMP OF DEBRIS, F.G.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON DEBRIS (FX) as it rolls over suddenly!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Now recognizable as the TERMINATOR'S HEAD AND ARMS, with half of the scattered torso trailing wires and twisted metal.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: IT LUNGES FOR HER!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah wants to scream this time, from the depths of her soul, but there is no scream, only a dry shivering sob.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Terminator drags itself SCRAPING over the floor, steel fingers clutching.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah is shaking and whimpering as she scrabbles away, crawling in agony.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON CONVEYOR BELT as Sarah flops from the catwalk onto the MOVING STRIP.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She is carried into the intricate lattice of equipment.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah rolls off weakly before going under a set of sorting rollers.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE THROUGH MACHINERY - ON THE TERMINATOR (FX) as it crawls after her, dragging its body.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It tracks her unerringly, EYES GLOWING.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah moves deeper into the DARK, CLASHING JUNGLE of machinery.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Around her is a rain-drenched tangle of CABLES, PIPES and unforgiving mechanisms of steel.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Terminator clambers through after her.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: C.U. - SARAH - Water pours into her eyes as she catches sight of something.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A familiar CONTROL BOX.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She drags herself toward it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: C.U. - THE TERMINATOR (FX) - It spots her wedged in a tiny crawl space.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: No way out.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It crawls the last few feet,EYES RED IN THE DARK.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Hypnotized, Sarah watches the Terminator REACHING TOWARD HER.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She is jammed in a corner.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah's hand claws around to the front of the control panel, seeking the RED BUTTON.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: E.C.U. - HER WET FINGERTIPS FEEL THE BUTTON.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON THE TERMINATOR (FX), his steel hand reaching out.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: E.C.U. - SARAH, her face inexplicably calm, eyes steady in that infinite instant.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She clenches her teeth to keep from screaming as she WAITS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Terminator's hand reaches for her throat to crush the life out of her and end its long mission.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SARAH
{META_DATA}: (voice icy)
{DIALOGUE}: You're...terminated...fucker!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: E.C.U. - BUTTON, as her bloody finger stabs it down.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: FULL SHOT, showing how the cyborg has been led into the MAW OF THE HYDRAULIC PRESS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: THE STAMPING PLATE THUNDERS DOWN!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Tons of mechanical pressure flatten the Terminator's head and body like tin-foil.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The PRESS SCREAMS, jamming solid.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Lightning snaps out in one brief blaze, leaping to surround- ing machinery, arcing to Sarah's wristwatch.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: All the Terminator's energy is released in one second.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE on the narrow gap between the upper and lower plates: a pinpoint of red light DWINDLES AND GOES OUT.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: TIGHT ON SARAH, shivering uncontrollably.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The steel fingers are frozen an inch from her throat.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She can only stare as water runs over her.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 257 INT. FACTORY - DAWN
